<seg id="63">Value added tax</seg>
<seg id="64">On 1 January 2005, the Council adopted Decision 5. 2004, the Czech Republic and the Czech Republic became members of the EU.</seg>
<seg id="65">After joining the EU, internal borders and border controls on the movement of goods within the EU were abolished.</seg>
