<seg id="364">In the same period, DR CLO from the Czech Republic adopted a total of 71 ŽOI and 7 SPI.</seg>
<seg id="365">Of the 71 received IO, 64 (i.e. 90.1 %) within the specified period of 3 months, 5 (i.e. 7.0%) was settled after this deadline (for the other 2 cases it was not possible to determine the time limit for the materials transmitted).</seg>
