<seg id="90">JCD entries from the customs databases of the Czech Republic and The Czech Republic were assigned to each other on the basis of the conformity of the individual paragraphs of the JCD (e.g. invoiced price, quantity, weight, registration number of the vehicle carrying the cargo, the date of crossing of the state border, the customs tariff item, etc.).</seg>
