<seg id="94">Other factors that influenced the success of the assignment were the different composition of data in the customs databases of the Czech Republic and The Czech Republic, as well as the time shift between the registration of exports in the customs database of one country and the records of the corresponding imports in the customs database of the other country.</seg>
<seg id="95">The results of the comparison were used in the selection of control samples at the audited financial and/or tax offices.</seg>
