<seg id="98">4.3. Pilot check at the Old Hrozenkov-Drietoma border customs crossing</seg>
<seg id="99">The border customs crossing for the pilot inspection was selected on the basis of a joint analysis of unassigned JCD items in the customs databases of the Czech Republic and The Slovak Republic.</seg>
<seg id="100">On the basis of a bilateral agreement between the customs authorities of the Czech Republic and the Czech Republic, the use of control sheets has been established at the border customs crossings between the Czech Republic and the Czech Republic since 1.6.1998.</seg>
<seg id="101">The aim of this measure was to eliminate customs and tax evasion as far as possible, to ensure an overview of the movement of means of transport carrying goods of a commercial nature in the customs area and to create the conditions for the comparison of customs records.</seg>
<seg id="102">The joint pilot control was carried out on 8 and 8 December 2004. 3. 2004 to 26. 3. 2004 and was aimed at examining this customs control system.</seg>
<seg id="103">Procedure for the use of control sheets at the Border Customs Crossing of The Stary Hrozenkov-Drietoma:</seg>
