<p>
<seg id="1">JOINT FINAL REPORT ON THE RESULTS OF PARALLEL CONTROLS ON EXCISE TAX ADMINISTRATION IN THE CZECH REPUBLIC</seg>
<seg id="2">Joint final report</seg>
<seg id="3">May 2017</seg>
<seg id="4">Supreme Audit Office of the Slovak Republic</seg>
<seg id="5">Supreme Audit Office of the Czech Republic</seg>
<seg id="6">Introductory word</seg>
<seg id="7">The present joint report informs about the progress and outcome of international cooperation in parallel checks carried out by the Supreme Audit Office of the Slovak Republic and the Supreme Audit Office of the Czech Republic, focusing on the management of excise duties in 2012-2015.</seg>
<seg id="8">Cooperation between the supreme control institutions of both countries was carried out on the basis of a cooperation agreement between the SAO SR and the SAO CR in the performance of parallel controls aimed at the administration of excise duties, which was concluded in August 2015.</seg>
