<seg id="14">The Supreme Audit Office, the Czech Republic (hereinafter referred to as the "SAO-CR") and the Najvyšší control office of the Slovak Republic (hereinafter referred to as the "SAO SR") concluded on 8 December 2004 that the Slovak Republic's audit authority, the Czech Republic, had concluded a joint agreement on 8 December 2004. The agreement on cooperation in control activities was not published in the Treaty of 2006.</seg>
