<seg id="17">The cooperation consisted of the exchange of information which the Contracting Parties could not obtain in the control of the management of excise duties in their territory and the preparation of a joint final report on the outcome of the checks within the meaning of the European Implementing Directives for the implementation of intosai audit standards - Directive 31.</seg>
<seg id="18">In the Czech Republic, the control (hereinafter referred to as "the Czech Republic") was carried out by groups of inspectors from the Department of the State Budget and from the territorial departments of Central Bohemia, South Bohemia, Western Bohemia, North-West Bohemia, South Moravia, Central Moravia and Northern Moravia between 7. Until 2 February 2005 They shall forthwith inform the</seg>
