<seg id="128">By checking these cases, the following were found to be:</seg>
<seg id="129">- 11 shipments of alcohol were recorded in the Slovak transport database in total quantities of 276.7 litres of alcohol carried out by the Czech tax entity in 2004 and 20 liters of alcohol transport in total in 2005.</seg>
